Real Estate in zip code 93437

Housing occupied 90.46% Housing vacant 9.54% Housing occupied by owner 0% Housing occupied by tenant 100% Total Rented Units 977 Median Contract Gross Rent $1,510 Median Gross Rent $1,540 Median Home Value $0

Contract rent is the monthly cash rent agreed to, regardless of any furnishings, utilities, fees, meals, or services that may be included. Gross rent is the contract rent plus the estimated average monthly cost of utilities and fuels if these are paid by the renter. In zip code 93437 median gross rent is 1.99% larger then the median contract rent.
